
### **7. SETUP SCRIPT: init_repo.sh**
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# init_repo.sh - Creates full 35-node architecture repository

echo "Creating 35-node architecture repository..."

# Create directory structure
mkdir -p 35-node-architecture/{validation,examples,evidence,docs}

# Core documents
echo "# 35-Node Sentient Lattice Architecture" > 35-node-architecture/ARCHITECTURE.md
echo "# Validation Methodology & Evidence" > 35-node-architecture/VALIDATION.md

# Reference E example
mkdir -p 35-node-architecture/examples
cat > 35-node-architecture/examples/reference_E_validation.md << 'EOF'
